spec_data.Name: perl-Class-ISA
spec_data.Description:
This library provides functions that return the list (in order) of names of
(super-)classes Perl would search to find a method, with no duplicates.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:55:19 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Report the search path for a class's ISA tree
